{"tid":2327252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府暫停發放許智峯區議員十二月三日後的薪俸","createTime":"2020-12-16T03:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T07:37:52.000Z","uid":22556,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"253a735f3d03dcd2e9f9fb396775ec1ae57cbec2","tid":2327252,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:00:33.000Z","msg":"民政事務總署指，會暫停發放許智峯在十二月三日或之後的酬金、津貼和開支償還款額，確保符合區議員薪津的指引，公帑得以妥善運用。<br />\n<br />\n目前區議員月薪3.5萬元，每月營運開支領4.6萬元，以及約八千元的雜項開支。<br />\n<br />\n政府暫停發放許智峯離港後區議員薪津<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416771&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416771%26refer%3DShare&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=7d248114\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416771%26refer%3DShare&h=b4fcef45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416771&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12c37e11bc187c86a91e916b43680f2290a5a4c1","tid":2327252,"uid":51583,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:02:09.000Z","msg":"你鍾意啦"},{"pid":"81b8a4951ae621e4bfeac28e347bf4dc49393b72","tid":2327252,"uid":152476,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:02:58.000Z","msg":"WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe0c738a4a5d5985b9d32cf3daeaeb9a4288f30","tid":2327252,"uid":376103,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"雖然唔可以用常理去解釋<br />\n<br />\n但其實憑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a033b507f07a9ab46c9166464bd7e8c70f52a8e","tid":2327252,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1fe0c738a4a5d5985b9d32cf3daeaeb9a4288f30","tid":2327252,"uid":376103,"like":2,"disli